nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.common

Interface TileInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TestTileInfo, TileInfo_Impl

    public interface TileInfo
    Contains info on tiles in the board. has a image and the name of the tile (name of class) and a map of fields in the tile class. For example if the Tile class has an id field the map of fields will contain key="id" value=the value of the id.
